<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="affect-vt">affect <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'fekt/    美 /ə'fekt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>影响</strong></h4>
<p>to influence sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>decisions which affect our lives 
影响我们生活的决定</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With the government’s aid, those (who were) affected by the earthquake have moved to the new settlements.
在政府的援助下，那些受到地震影响的人已经搬到新的定居点。</p><footer>2009 上海改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>使感动；打动</strong></h4>
<p>to make sb have strong feelings of sadness, pity, etc.：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was <strong>deeply affected</strong> by the story. 
她被这个故事深深打动了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>使感染 (疾病)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Diseases affect almost everyone at some time during their lives.
生活中几乎每个人都会生病。</p><footer>译林⑦ – 2</footer></div></div>